text: Adell is a village of Sheboygan County, Wisconsin, United States. The population is 498 people as of 2020. Adell has an area of .6 square miles, thanks to the United States Census Bureau. Hildegarde, an American cabaret singer, was born in Adell. ==References== Category:Villages in Wisconsin Category:Sheboygan County, Wisconsin
title: Adell, Wisconsin
